    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Women who cohabit with a man without being his wife. The term today has a negative connotation, and is generally only used in the context of certain historical periods, particularly in Asia or ancient times.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
